for eg, in this 

    array = {8,10,5}
max is 10 and min is 5.

Then you subtract the difference  (5) from the maximum and its adjacent and ignoring the value which is in less adjacent.( in this case, neighbours of 10 are 8,5 -&gt; therefore, subtract 5 from 8) ,then  

       arrays ={3,5,5} 

now again iterate the array and find max and min ( 5,3) 
. Subtract the difference ( 5-3 =2 ) from the max and its adjcent neighbour with more value ( from 3,5  , subtract 2 from 5 ) 
